  "title": "Staff Nurse - Urology Specialist Clinic| Office Hours - 5.5 Days - Up to $4k (0580)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Salary: $2500 - $4000</li>\n  <li>Working hours: 5.5 days; Mon - Fri: 9:00am - 5pm, Sat: 9:00am - 1pm</li>\n  <li>Location: Mount Elizabeth Novena Hospital, Gleneagles Medical Centre (Rotate between 2 locations)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Undertake nursing duties (i.e. phlebotomy, subcutaneous/intramuscular injections, simple wound dressings)</li>\n  <li>Medication dispensing</li>\n  <li>Chaperone doctor, assist with minor procedures in clinic</li>\n  <li>Perform administrative duties including patient registration, payments, booking of appointments, financial counselling, stock-taking and managing insurance claims.</li>\n  <li>Ensure the cleanliness and tidiness of the clinic</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree / Diploma / Nitec in Nursing</li>\n  <li>Full registration under Singapore Nursing Board</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p>\n<p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
